				<wikidot:authorName>Khaim</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1796098</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>If you see an SCP-5310 standing in a hallway or in the break room or something, that’s fine, it’s supposed to be there. If you see them all standing on the hill outside, that’s not fine, they’re not supposed to be there, go get someone immediately.</p> </blockquote> <p>I love this part so much. I don't know why.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
