					<![CDATA[
						 <p>No idea what's going on here. Is that the point? I don't know. But it's well written and I like to imagine that the foundation has some perfectly reasonable explanation somewhere, in a separate document, of what exactly this all means and why it's written that way. Of course, letting us see it would ruin the fun, wouldn't it? +1</p> 
				 	]]>
